			"updated": 1777281977779,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "EC2 service:\n    Image + Image build service\n        - [ ] admin dashboard for managing resources\n    Instance service\n        - [ ] creating & running & deleting\n        - [ ] attaching to terminal\n        - [ ] users able to deploy (bonus)\n    User dashboard\n        - [ ] management + view\n        - [ ] statistics (bonus)\n\nHome app\n    - [ ] landing page\n    - [ ] link to reg/log in/dashboard\n\nUser management app\n    - [ ] customize django auth",
			"rawText": "EC2 service:\n    Image + Image build service\n        - [ ] admin dashboard for managing resources\n    Instance service\n        - [ ] creating & running & deleting\n        - [ ] attaching to terminal\n        - [ ] users able to deploy (bonus)\n    User dashboard\n        - [ ] management + view\n        - [ ] statistics (bonus)\n\nHome app\n    - [ ] landing page\n    - [ ] link to reg/log in/dashboard\n\nUser management app\n    - [ ] customize django auth",
			"fontSize": 36,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "EC2 service:\n    Image + Image build service\n        - [ ] admin dashboard for managing resources\n    Instance service\n        - [ ] creating & running & deleting\n        - [ ] attaching to terminal\n        - [ ] users able to deploy (bonus)\n    User dashboard\n        - [ ] management + view\n        - [ ] statistics (bonus)\n\nHome app\n    - [ ] landing page\n    - [ ] link to reg/log in/dashboard\n\nUser management app\n    - [ ] customize django auth",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
