			"updated": 1777282119454,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "An assignee must implement:\n    - service\n    - templates for it\n    - styling + js\n    - documentation\n\nEC2: 3 apps => 3 people\n\nHome app + User mgmt app => 1 person (because each is light)",
			"rawText": "An assignee must implement:\n    - service\n    - templates for it\n    - styling + js\n    - documentation\n\nEC2: 3 apps => 3 people\n\nHome app + User mgmt app => 1 person (because each is light)",
