			"versionNonce": 1613540488,
			"isDeleted": false,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1777284493931,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "1. Home app + user mgmt app = independent\n\n2. image = depends on image build\n\n3. [image + image build] = independent as a whole\n\n4. instance = depends on [image + image build]\n5. s3 service = independent\n6. docker_ops\n\nBuilding order:\n\n1-2-5 parallel to each and to 3-4,\n6->3->4",
			"rawText": "1. Home app + user mgmt app = independent\n\n2. image = depends on image build\n\n3. [image + image build] = independent as a whole\n\n4. instance = depends on [image + image build]\n5. s3 service = independent\n6. docker_ops\n\nBuilding order:\n\n1-2-5 parallel to each and to 3-4,\n6->3->4",
			"fontSize": 36,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "1. Home app + user mgmt app = independent\n\n2. image = depends on image build\n\n3. [image + image build] = independent as a whole\n\n4. instance = depends on [image + image build]\n5. s3 service = independent\n6. docker_ops\n\nBuilding order:\n\n1-2-5 parallel to each and to 3-4,\n6->3->4",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false,
			"link": null
		},
